{
  "stem": "1387.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I keep thinking, constantly, that maybe if he had gotten to the camp in Sasow, back, maybe he would have survived this-- the-- the war-- the war, like I was lucky to do.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it's it's something that-- that comes to my mind often.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Also, I'd like to mention to you that Sasow is known of its own rebellion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sasow camp, when they saw they were bringing-- Sasow camp was located in a estate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] There was a paper factory in Sasow, years back, and the owner of that factory lived in that estate where the-- where the [NON-ENGLISH] was situated.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When they surrounded the camp in Sasow, they took individuals and they brought them into the estate, into the building, and they were shooting them there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some people in the Sasow camp rebelled.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They called, [NON-ENGLISH], and they started running in all directions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some 50-- over 50 people succeeded in running through the barbed wires into the woods.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Many of them were killed in the woods, and I know of 17 that succeeded in saving their lives.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They ran away in the area of the same woods that I was hiding in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some of them are caught-- were caught [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] because the-- the front line between the Soviet Union and Germany changed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, the-- the Soviets were in that part of the woods, and the next day, the Germans came back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were caught in-- in-- in one of those fights, and some of them got killed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But some of them survived, and they survived only because they had the courage to run away.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
